						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into a wall Prānti office.</p>						

						<p>Ibrāhim II A.D. 1598.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in Śaka 1520, Viḷambi, Kārttika śu. 7, corresponding to A.D. 1598, November 25, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>It records the excavation of a well near the village Nīlage by Khāneājam Khursitakhān, the chief of Baṅkāpur fort, for the merit of king.</p>						

						</summary>
