<p>
<lb n="1"/>ṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmatu jayābhyudayaśālivāhanaśakava
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ruṣa 1520 neya viḷaṁbināmasaṁvatsarada kā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rtika śudha 7 yalu hajarayitibarāyima Adalu śā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>pādaśahāsāhēbarige puṁṇyavāgabēkeṁdu baṁkāpu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rada durgādhipati khāneAjaṁkhurasitakhānaru nīlage grā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mada samīpadalli sumuhūrthadiṁda kaṭṭisida bāvige maṁgaḷa mahā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ślōka <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> vāpīkūpataṭākādiṁ kartumichaṁti yē narāṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Araṁ<unclear>ṇyē</unclear>
<lb n="8"/>nirjarē dēśē pathichāyādivarjitē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tatra kurvaṁti yē
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lōkā dharmanirvāṇa saṁgrahaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tatsarvaṁ kathayiṣyāmi sa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rvapuṁṇyēṣu yōdhikaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tathāḥ yāvaśvaṁdraśya sūryaśya yā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vattiṣṭaṁtti mēdinī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tatpuṁṇyāni varddhaṁti tē vasaṁti nabhastalē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> dha
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rmakāryēṣu vighnāni yē kurvaṁti narādhamā tē vasaṁti yamaḥ
<lb n="13"/>ghōrē ravaravē narakē sadā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 5 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śubhaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
</p>

